'''聖索菲亞教堂'''（{{lang-mk|Црква Света Софија}}）是位於[[馬其頓共和國|馬其頓共和國]][[奧赫里德|奧赫里德]]的一座教堂。聖索菲亞教堂修建於第一保加利亞帝國時期<ref>Boris Cholpanov - 	
"Land of a global crossroads", Sofia, 1993, Bulgarian Academy of Science, page 131 (the original is in Bulgarian)</ref>。聖索菲亞教堂也被印刷在1000馬其頓第納爾的鈔票上<ref>[http://www.nbrm.gov.mk National Bank of the Republic of Macedonia] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nbrm.gov.mk/ |date=20080819150726 }}. Macedonian currency. Banknotes in circulation: [http://www.nbrm.gov.mk/default-en.asp?ItemID=6952ADD956EBFB459A15A404C33CC691 1000 Denars]{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} (1996 issue) & [http://www.nbrm.gov.mk/default-en.asp?ItemID=DE6805545764DF4A8895DE62BFA0151D 1000 Denars] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080329135028/http://www.nbrm.gov.mk/default-en.asp?ItemID=DE6805545764DF4A8895DE62BFA0151D |date=2008-03-29 }} (2003 issue). – Retrieved on 30 March 2009.</ref>。
